column5: Had a chance to get for some soft water action.
Those jumbos really look tasty - Lake Erie I presume?  What depth ya fishing at - picture doesn't look like your to far out.  Don
Oh my god look at the guts on those things - they look like they're about to pop!  Good job!  Cheers, Ryan
Nice Job! Looks like your going to have a good dinner tonight!
court r hasn't replied to any of the posts so maybe the bellies did explode on him--lol either that or he's to full to chat.......
Ya, that's Erie..the fish were scattered 40'-70'.
